<p><span class="anchor" id="p26"></span>فخذ من البو عباس بالعراق.<a href="#p26" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p27"></span>العزاوي ٤/ ٢٥١<a href="#p27" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
